" Keybindings {{{
" Emacs style beginnig and end of line in insert mode
imap <C-e> <esc>$a
imap <C-a> <esc>^i
" select paste text
nnoremap gp `[v`]
" go to end of selection after yank
vmap y ygv<Esc>
" " use some unused function key codes to
" " make special key combos work in terminal
map  <F13> <M-Up>
map  <F14> <M-Down>

nmap <silent> cog :GitGutterToggle<CR>
